FBIS3-28451 "dreas025_c_94030" FBIS-EAS-94-025 Document Type:Daily Report 7 Feb 1994 North Korea Kim Il-song Sends Wreath to Bier of Yi Tu-su SK0502112694 Pyongyang KCNA in English 1046 GMT 5 Feb 94 SK0502112694 Pyongyang KCNA Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] Pyongyang, February 5 (KCNA) -- The great leader President Kim Il-song today sent a wreath to the bier of Comrade Yi Tu-su, an anti-Japanese revolutionary fighter, expressing deep condolences over his death.
